\hat{d}_{C}^{U}=\binom{R}{2}^{-1}\sum_{i\neq i}\sum_{j<k}l(X_{ij},X_{i'k})R_{ij}R_{i'k}\hat{\pi}_{j}^{-1}\hat{\pi}_{k}^{-1}
\]

